reviewText: This is a great movie. Disney & Pixar don't go wrong. this movie is awesome I love this movie. the Incredibles is about a dysfunctional superhero family who been kicked out of society for saving someone's life who didn't want to be saved. now Mr. incredible is on a mission to regain peoples faith in superheroes. If you have not seen this movie then I recommend you do. This movie is Cinematastic
It arrived on time. It didn't skip.
